reviewText: been watchin van since abt 74/75 when i caught him at at a a club in dallas,the binary star,was very impressed. my only complaint is this dvd is only 8 tracks, we wantie more senor van ! its a good dvd i would buy it again. thx van from rico in reno tejas

I used to play bass for Van and I have watched him grow into the virtuoso perfomer he is today.  He has all the licks and is a creative songwriter.  Texas Rock "n" Roll and Blues lives on with guys like Van reminding us of why we are Texans for life no matter where we stand.
